1962;;House of Women;;American;;Crane Wilbur;;Shirley Knight, Andrew Duggan, Constance Ford;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/House_of_Women;;Erica Hayden (Knight) is a young expectant mother who is wrongly implicated in a crime and sent to prison for five years. Erica learns that she must find a guardian for her daughter or she will become a ward of the state. The prison's warden, Frank Cole (Duggan), becomes infatuated with Erica and effectively blocks her chances for a parole.<br><br>When another inmate's child dies, the woman becomes deranged. Erica prevents a tragedy and earns the right to be freed to be with her daughter, while the Warden Cole's unethical methods come to light.